{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4bcb31f38e","title":"复西北各族人民抗美援朝代表会议电","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"345f4c036d","index":0,"year":1951,"month":12,"day":12,"articleId":"4bcb31f38e"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji31","name":"毛泽东全集第31卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/31-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji31":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"f1ea7745ec","type":"title","text":"复西北各族人民抗美援朝代表会议电","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"4bcb31f38e"},{"id":"30fbc031b8","type":"paragraph","text":"西北各族人民抗美援朝代表会议全体代表同志们：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"4bcb31f38e"},{"id":"bc4a848bd5","type":"paragraph","text":"感谢你们给我的电报。过去一年多以来，西北区各族人民在抗美援朝的爱国斗争中，作了很大的努力，得到了很大的成绩。你们的这次代表会议，决定进一步团结各族人民，增加生产，厉行节约，开展爱国主义的宣传教育工作，以支持中国人民志愿军，这是很好的。帝国主义过去敢于欺负中国的原因之一，是中国各民族不团结，但是这个时代已经永远过去了，从中华人民共和国成立的那一天起，中国各民族就开始团结成为友爱合作的大家庭，足以战胜任何帝国主义的侵略，并且把我们的祖国建设成为繁荣强盛的国家。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"4bcb31f38e"},{"id":"b07114b7b1","type":"paragraph","text":"祝你们的会议成功！","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"4bcb31f38e"},{"id":"708f201a69","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"4bcb31f38e"},{"id":"92c3b2c472","type":"paragraph","text":"十二月十二日","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"4bcb31f38e"}],"page":{"id":"a65b5445a9","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"4bcb31f38e","start":129,"end":129}}}},"__N_SSG":true}